---
import TalleyPage from '../../../components/talley-wealth/TalleyPage.astro';
---

<TalleyPage title="Your Guide Is Ready | Talley Wealth" description="Download your Talley Wealth retirement planning guide." noindex>
  <section class="bg-muted/35">
    <div class="section-container grid min-h-[620px] items-center gap-12 py-20 lg:grid-cols-[0.85fr_1fr]">
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent">Guide download</p>
        <h1 class="mt-5 max-w-2xl font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-primary md:text-5xl">Your guide is ready.</h1>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
          Download <em>Are You Actually On Track?</em>, a plain-English framework for understanding what your retirement number really means.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="/brands/talley-wealth/guides/are-you-on-track.pdf" class="rounded-md bg-accent px-5 py-3 font-bold text-accent-foreground">Download the PDF</a>
          <a href="/calculators" class="rounded-md border border-border bg-background px-5 py-3 font-bold text-primary">Run the calculator</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-6 shadow-elegant md:p-8">
        <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent">Suggested order</p>
        <div class="mt-6 divide-y divide-border">
          <div class="py-4">
            <p class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-primary">1. Read the guide</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-muted-foreground">Get the framework before trying to solve the whole problem with one number.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="py-4">
            <p class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-primary">2. Run the calculator</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-muted-foreground">Use your numbers to see the rough gap, surplus, or pressure points.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="py-4">
            <p class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-primary">3. Talk through the tradeoffs</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-muted-foreground">If the questions get more specific, an Explore Call is the next step.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</TalleyPage>
